<header class="nyasa-header">
<h1 class="nyasa-title">Malawi President visits flood victims and distributes relief goods</h1> <div class="entry-meta">
<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></span> March 13, 2019
<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"> </span> Kondwani Magombo -Mana <a href="https://www.nyasatimes.com/malawi-president-visits-flood-victims-and-distributes-relief-goods/#comments"> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"> </span> 21 Comments </a>
</div>
</header>
<div class="nyasa-content">
<p>President Peter Mutharika  on Tuesday  started visiting areas affected by floods that have rendered about 114 000 people in about 10 districts in the country destitute and has assured people wthat government would do everything it could to ensure that they have all the necessary humanitarian support required.</p>
<figure id="attachment_159778" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-159778" style="width: 600px" class="wp-caption alignright"><noscript><img  data-lazy-  alt width="600" height="400" data-srcset="https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056.jpg 1080w"  data-src="https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" class="size-large wp-image-159778 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw=="><noscript><img src="https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056-600x400.jpg" class="size-large wp-image-159778" alt width="600" height="400" srcset="https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px"></noscript></noscript><img src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20600%20400%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056-600x400.jpg" class="lazyload size-large wp-image-159778" alt width="600" height="400" data-srcset="https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.nyasatimes.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20190313-WA0056.jpg 1080w" data-sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px"><noscript><img   alt="" width="600" height="4