</div>
</div>
<div class="wpd-comment-text">
<p>The President is turning the plight of the flood victims into a political opportunity with a view to the forthcoming elections. This is wrong and unbecoming of the Head of State. Most of these people were already suffering from poverty before the floods due to DPP government incompetence and mismanagement. Too little, too late, Mr President.</p>
